{"tid":653668,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【尊嚴何價】低調地產經紀扮狗爬 一字排開俾女經理含淚摑？","createTime":"2018-05-05T02:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T04:23:39.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1a87f8e992e3a420c75a605977b13361458a4dff","tid":653668,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T02:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180505/58150460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F58150460&d=NtOywCjt9gxtgongQE2YAFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=0f7526dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F58150460&h=2ce3fea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180505/58150460</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180504/large/1525447467_f932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180504%2Flarge%2F1525447467_f932.jpg&h=7c878a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尊嚴何價？湖北宜昌房產銷售公司員工的「培訓」影片流出網絡，引發網民熱議。片段中，身穿制服的女職員掌摑6名男地產經紀；數十名員工圍成一圈在地上學狗爬；還有被罰兔仔跳，簡直「瘋狂」。<br />\n<br />\n網民文先生2日打開微信，接連有好友向他發出3段「培訓」影片，一群穿着制服的職員在街頭邊跳邊高呼口號，還有職員在辦公室扮狗爬。最離譜的是，女職員含淚用力掌摑6名排成一排的男同事，其中一名戴着眼鏡的男子當場被打飛。<br />\n一位業內人士透露，該公司的做法借鑑了宜昌同行一公司的「經驗」。影片中的員工因種種原因對此敢怒不敢言。<br />\n房產銷售公司負責人胡先生承認是該公司員工，但影片內容並非員工培訓，而是一門市4月份的月度業務會。他表示，已確定影片是公司另一個門市的經理，拍攝的初衷是準備給自己下屬看，沒想到影片從公司內部流出到網絡。<br />\n胡先生解釋：「網友議論最多的掌摑視頻，大家可以發現，其中的女員工揮手時是含着淚的。事實是，這6名男員工未按照公司要求履職，例如未向客戶打電話等等。僅僅是因為工作狀態太鬆弛，與他們的業績毫無關係。月度會上，門市女經理張女士問下屬如何處罰，男員工自己要求打臉。」<br />\n胡先生認為，這些傳言中不乏同行惡意攻擊。他稱其公司目前有10多間門市、160多名員工，在宜昌同行中實力雄厚，而同行之間競爭十分激烈。他更指，公司至今對網傳的影片不發聲，並不代表放棄維權的權利。因為視頻傳播面太廣，影片中掌摑同事的女經理礙於壓力，已於周三（2日）離職回家休息。"},{"pid":"69f091a4f68c541082f69df4991d35bfd2064cd4","tid":653668,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T02:42:48.000Z","msg":"好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8c4df75171e3fda1663e6f39ea777b876b245b","tid":653668,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69f091a4f68c541082f69df4991d35bfd2064cd4","tid":653668,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T02:42:48.000Z","msg":"好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T02:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f38938a7db321946c10693eb7322e79fbdf9ac4","tid":653668,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"做得地產就預咗咁低賤架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc243e6fe31bf757289442cf4b5ac4f10bf0d1c4","tid":653668,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:01:48.000Z","msg":"間公司仲諗咩撚野維權"},{"pid":"01c4c6c5d4a3e1d1ac1f3b3c61dc49067013d7ab","tid":653668,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1d06553c33630a606941be438dbc895962f10d","tid":653668,"uid":116688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"打死晒咪啱，有咩好討論"},{"pid":"42f84a02884754ae75be6005fafcb5c67f6ccaa1","tid":653668,"uid":171058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"班賤種5毛狗平時都可能係咁<br />\n歪理唔夠歪，就排隊掌摑<br />\n唯一分別係牠們唔使 &quot;扮狗&quot;<br />\n因為本身已經keep住爬"},{"pid":"57c8db8a042674e3926685c1996c7ddef5a83e53","tid":653668,"uid":90863,"like":0,"d